title: The Price of Perfection with Violet Chachki
description:
The legendary, incomparable, and flawless Violet Chachki talks spiraling from hanger, having an Attitude, and Drag Race memories. 
Get ready for immense amounts of shade, lots of reading, and several harsh truths about what it takes to be absolutely perfect. 

To follow Violet: @VioletChachki
To follow Trixie: @TrixieMattel
To follow Katya: @Katya_Zamo
To listen to our podcast on YouTube: http://bit.ly/TBATBYT
